if you prefer consistent spelling in tooling and links.

External calls from the browser (all free, no auth required):
  - raw.githubusercontent.com or GitHub Release URL – for the .fgb
  - raw.githubusercontent.com – for coefficient CSVs (CORS-enabled)
  - https://geo.api.gouv.fr – geocoding (open API, no key)


